This course focuses on discussing how to use the generalized linear models to analyze the data. There are several topics will be discussed:
GLM, L S method, Weighted  L S method, M L method, linear regression model, nonlinear regression models, Logistic and Poisson regression models, and so on.

content:
Linear regression; Support vector regression (SVR); Random forest regression; 
Deep learning models such as RNN; LSTM; GRU; convolution; 
Deep learning for computer vision; Deep learning for text and sequences; 
Advanced deep learning best practices; Generative deep learning.
Real cases for forecasting problems.

